        <item>
          <title>Nvidia Confirms Pre-Order Date for RTX 50 Series Laptops - A Gamers' Paradise</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Nvidia has confirmed that pre-orders for RTX 50 series laptops will go live from February 25, with shipping expected to commence in March. This development comes on the heels of Nvidia's CES 2025 announcement, where the company showcased its Blackwell mobile GPUs.]]></description>
